### Create a new contact
POST http://localhost:2000/contacts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Alice",
  "lastName": "Nanyonga",
  "email": "alice@example.com",
  "favoriteColor": "Yellow",
  "birthday": "1995-05-12"
}

###

### Update a contact
PUT http://localhost:2000/contacts/65123456789abcdef0123456
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Job",
  "lastName": "Talemwa",
  "email": "jobtalemwa_new@example.com",
  "favoriteColor": "Blue",
